18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1-8-113 of Title 10A, unless
20 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 If there is cause to believe a crime has been committed,
22 pursuant to Sections 1111 or 1123 of Title 21 of the Oklahoma
23 Statutes, by an employee or contractor of the Department of Human
24 Services against a child who is under the legal custody,
